{
  "stem": "15396.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not so many funny things in Marseille at that time, but when one did, it was so hilarious that it got around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, some of these people knowing that they were right on the verge of death anyway, of being caught, had a surprising sense of humor, some of them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember one or two.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Klaus Dohrn was one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Konrad Heiden.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know who these people were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had no idea, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were just-- just numbers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I went back to hospital and stayed quite a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, back in the States then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first place that I went in was back in France, the first hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I didn't have any money, and I had TB, and it had it on my discharge, pulmonary tuberculosis, I think in red ink if I'm not mistaken.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so nobody-- I remember a woman, when I was applying for a job, opened the window when I left to shoo the germs out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was painting signs in the [INAUDIBLE] to make a living, and I knew a lot of people in France, in Paris, but I didn't want to look like-- I looked like death warmed over.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I ran into a man, a journalist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That story I told you about, the little boy?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the first story I told him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wanted to know-- he saw me, what was left over of a Legion uniform, and he wanted to know why and all that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to mislead him, I told him stories about people.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
